<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{كلا نمد هَؤُلَاءِ وَهَؤُلَاء}</span> يَعْنِي: الْمُؤْمِنِينَ وَالْمُشْرِكِينَ إِلَى قَوْلِهِ: <span class="c3">{مَحْظُورًا}</span> أَيْ مَمْنُوعًا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُحَمَّدٌ:</span> <span class="c2">(كُلًّا)</span> مَنْصُوب ب <span class="c2">(نمد)</span> و <span class="c2">(هَؤُلَاءِ)</span> بَدَلٌ مِنْ <span class="c2">(كُلِّ)</span> الْمَعْنَى: نُمِدُّ هَؤُلَاءِ وَهَؤُلَاء.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>